### POST request with missing event field - should return 400 Bad Request
POST http://localhost:28852/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2021-02-10"
}

###

### POST request with missing date field - should return 400 Bad Request
POST http://localhost:28852/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "Video conference"
}

###

### POST request with both event and date fields - should return 200 OK
POST http://localhost:28852/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "Video conference",
  "date": "2020-11-15"
}

